---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Grade 4 Summary | Aarya Patel">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 space-y-6">

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="text-center py-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">📖 Grade 4 Chronicle</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">My journey through 4th grade - what I learned and achieved</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Year Overview -->
    <Card title="Welcome to My Grade 4 Story!" emoji="🌟">
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        Grade 4 was an amazing year! I learned so much, tried new things, and had fun along the way.
        Here's a look at everything I accomplished.
      </p>
    </Card>

    <!-- Books Section -->
    <Card title="📚 Books I Read" emoji="">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold">Basic English Grammar for Dummies</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">By Willies Publication</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            My first proper textbook! This was my first time reading a textbook cover to cover.
            I learned grammar fundamentals that help me write better.
          </p>
          <a href="/topics/books" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline text-sm mt-2 inline-block">Read my review →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold">Creative Problem Solving in School Mathematics</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">By George Lencher</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            An amazing math book that taught me creative problem-solving strategies.
            The puzzles were challenging but so satisfying to solve!
          </p>
          <a href="/topics/books" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline text-sm mt-2 inline-block">Read my review →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Card>

    <!-- Coding Section -->
    <Card title="💻 Coding Journey" emoji="">
      <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <p><strong>Python Programming:</strong> Mastered the basics!</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-sm">
          <li>Data types: numbers, strings, lists, sets, dictionaries</li>
          <li>Conditionals and loops</li>
          <li>Functions and reusable code</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-4"><strong>LeetCode:</strong> Solved 140+ problems!</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Regular practice helps me think logically and learn new algorithms.</p>

        <p class="mt-4"><strong>First Game:</strong> Built a Snake Game!</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Used Python and Pygame to create a playable game that runs in the browser.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="/topics/coding" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline text-sm mt-3 inline-block">See my coding journey →</a>
    </Card>

    <!-- Math Section -->
    <Card title="🧮 Math & Competitions" emoji="">
      <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <p><strong>Kangaroo Math Competition:</strong> Scored 76/120</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3">
          This was my first competitive math exam! I learned that:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-sm">
          <li>Practice tests don't always predict real test performance</li>
          <li>Test-taking is a skill that takes practice</li>
          <li>One score doesn't define my abilities</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm">
          <em>Important lesson: Exams can be tricky even when you're well prepared. I'm proud of myself for trying!</em>
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="/topics/math" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline text-sm mt-3 inline-block">Read more about my math journey →</a>
    </Card>

    <!-- Other Interests -->
    <Card title="🎹 Music & Other Interests" emoji="">
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li><strong>Piano:</strong> Continued playing and practicing</li>
        <li><strong>Art:</strong> Explored creative projects</li>
        <li><strong>Problem Solving:</strong> Always looking for new challenges</li>
      </ul>
    </Card>

    <!-- Reflection -->
    <Card title="💭 What Grade 4 Taught Me" emoji="">
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>Hard work pays off - whether it's coding, math, or piano</li>
        <li>It's okay to not get everything right the first time</li>
        <li>Learning is a journey, not a destination</li>
        <li>Trying new things (like competitions) helps me grow</li>
        <li>Balancing different interests makes life interesting!</li>
      </ul>
    </Card>

    <!-- Looking Ahead -->
    <Card title="🚀 Ready for Grade 5!" emoji="">
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        Grade 4 was amazing, but I'm excited for what's next! Grade 5 brings new challenges,
        new things to learn, and more opportunities to grow.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
        Check back during Grade 5 to see my progress!
      </p>
    </Card>

    <!-- Back to Home -->
    <div class="text-center pt-4">
      <a href="/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
